Pursuant to regulation 29(1) of SEBI (Listing Obligations and Disclosure Requirements) Regulations 2015 it is to inform you that the meeting of the Board of Directors of the Company is scheduled to be held on Wednesday May 28 2025 inter alia for considering and approving the following:

1. Standalone Audited Financial Results of the company for the quarter and year ended 31st March 2025;

2. Recommend a final dividend on the equity shares if any.
